Paul Brinegar https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Brinegar 0 Paul Alden Brinegar Jr. (December 19, 1917 – March 27, 1995) was an American character actor best known for his roles in three western series: The Life and Legend of Wyatt Earp, Rawhide, and Lancer.
